      <title>阿联酋法院以恐怖主义罪名判处 50 多人有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uae-court-convicts-more-than-50-people-on-terrorism-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国以恐怖主义罪名判处 50 多人有罪，指控他们与被指定为海湾国家恐怖组织的穆斯林兄弟会合作并活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uae-court-convicts-more-than-50-people-on-terrorism-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:47:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚将取消部分食品进口关税以抑制通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/nigeria-fights-high-food-costs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚宣布了一系列措施来抑制食品通胀。该国食品通胀正以 30 年来最快的速度上涨，该国 2 亿多人口中近一半生活在极端贫困中。彭博新闻社的 Ruth Olurounbi 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/nigeria-fights-high-food-costs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:44:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国央行行长警告下届政府不要扩大赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/bank-of-france-chief-warns-against-widening-country-s-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国各政党竞相组建下一届政府之际，法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛警告称，法国不能承受赤字持续增加或企业承担更多税收和成本的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/bank-of-france-chief-warns-against-widening-country-s-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:27:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示瑞典长期通胀预期略有上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/swedish-long-term-inflation-expectations-edge-higher-in-survey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Prospera 的最新调查显示，由于瑞典央行已开始降低借贷成本，市场对瑞典长期通胀率的预期略高于瑞典央行 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/swedish-long-term-inflation-expectations-edge-higher-in-survey</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国水务与水务管理局拒绝提高水费，泰晤士水务公司可能被解散</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/thames-water-put-in-special-measures-regime-by-industry-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据监管机构 Ofwat 周四提出的特别措施计划，英国最大的水务和污水处理公司可能会被拆分、在证券交易所上市或被迫限制其债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/thames-water-put-in-special-measures-regime-by-industry-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 5 月份经济增长 0.4%，为预期增速的两倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-economy-rebounds-faster-than-expected-on-construction-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国五月份经济增速是预期的两倍，表明新工党政府正依赖强劲经济实力来资助其让国家恢复运转的雄心勃勃的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-economy-rebounds-faster-than-expected-on-construction-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国原油库存减少提振市场人气，油价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于需求增长的迹象和整个市场的风险偏好共同提振了市场人气，油价连续第二天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:28:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
